{"inkVersion":19,"root":[[{"->":"opening"},["done",{"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"opening":[[{"#":"music ambient_hum"},{"#":"visual black"},"^Dark. Pressure. Dirt in your mouth.","\n","^A question surfaces — not yours.","\n","^<i>What's the reward for getting stronger?</i>","\n","ev","str","^Getting to rest","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^Never resting again","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},"ev","str","^I don't know","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n","ev",{"VAR?":"karma"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"karma","re":true},"/ev",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},null],"c-1":["\n","ev",{"VAR?":"karma"},1,"-",{"VAR=":"karma","re":true},"/ev",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},null],"c-2":["\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},null],"g-0":["^<i>Noted.</i>","\n",{"#":"visual fade_white"},{"->":"room1_greenhouse"},null]}],null],"room1_greenhouse":[[{"#":"music glass_drip"},{"#":"visual greenhouse_broken"},"^Glass ceiling. Broken pots. You're lying in soil.","\n",{"#":"anim standup"},"^A sheet of cracked glass blocks the exit. There's a gap at the bottom — tight.","\n","ev","str","^Throw a heavy shard at the glass","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^Crawl through the gap","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},{"c-0":["^ ",{"#":"sound shatter"},"\n",{"#":"anim throw"},"^Glass explodes. Clean exit.","\n","^<b>VOICE:</b> efficient. i like that.","\n",{"->":"room2_path"},null],"c-1":["^ ",{"#":"anim crawl"},"\n","^Scrape through. Glass scratches your back.","\n","^<b>VOICE:</b> taking the hard way. that's very you.","\n","^<i>Who—</i>","\n","^Silence.","\n",{"->":"room2_path"},null]}],null],"room2_path":[[{"#":"music garden_wind"},{"#":"visual tangled_vines"},"^Vines block the path. Green (alive) and brown (brittle).","\n","ev","str","^Pull green vine","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^Pull brown vine","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n",{"#":"sound crash"},"^Debris falls. Wrong choice. The brown vine is now exposed.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.brown"},null],"c-1":["\n",{"->":".^.^.^.brown"},null]}],{"brown":[[{"#":"sound crumble"},"^The brown vine disintegrates. A gap opens.","\n",{"#":"visual sunlit_clearing"},"^Beyond: a small clearing. Sunlight breaks through. In the center, floating at chest height — a golden-yellow petal, glowing faintly.","\n","^<i>It feels warm. Like summer morning.</i>","\n","ev","str","^Reach for the petal","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^Leave it","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n","ev",1,"/ev",{"VAR=":"has_joy_petal","re":true},"ev",{"VAR?":"karma"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"karma","re":true},"/ev",{"#":"anim touch_petal"},{"#":"visual joy_glow"},"^The petal dissolves into your palm. Warmth spreads through your chest.","\n","^<i>Joy. That's what this is. You'd almost forgotten.</i>","\n","^<b>VOICE:</b> ah. comfort. enjoy it while it lasts.","\n",["ev","str","^Comfort?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^Say nothing","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n","^<b>VOICE:</b> comfort is easy. cheap pleasure. real satisfaction requires struggle. you'll learn the difference.","\n","^<i>The warmth stays, but something feels... off.</i>","\n",{"->":"room3_bridge"},null],"c-1":["\n",{"->":"room3_bridge"},null]}],null],"c-1":["\n","^<i>Just light. Probably nothing.</i>","\n",{"->":"room3_bridge"},null]}],null]}],"room3_bridge":[[{"#":"music wind_silence"},{"#":"visual rotten_bridge"},"^A wooden bridge over a deep, dry ravine. Planks rotted. Some missing.","\n","^<i>Something tightens in your chest.</i>","\n","^<b>VOICE:</b> you're afraid. that's weakness showing.","\n","ev","str","^No, it's not weakness","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^Maybe you're right","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},"ev","str","^I don't know what this is","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n","ev",1,"/ev",{"VAR=":"fear_understood","re":true},"ev",{"VAR?":"voice_trust"},1,"-",{"VAR=":"voice_trust","re":true},"/ev","^<i>Fear isn't weakness. It's a warning. The bridge IS dangerous.</i>","\n","^<b>VOICE:</b> ...hm. maybe.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.cross"},null],"c-1":["\n","ev",1,"/ev",{"VAR=":"fear_mislabeled","re":true},"ev",{"VAR?":"voice_trust"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"voice_trust","re":true},"/ev","^<i>The voice knows more than you. Probably.</i>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.cross"},null],"c-2":["\n",{"->":".^.^.^.cross"},null]}],{"cross":[["^<b>VOICE:</b> fear says: run. or freeze. never helpful.","\n","^<i>But fear is WHY you're being careful. It's trying to keep you alive.</i>","\n","ev","str","^Run across fast","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^Walk slowly, testing each plank","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n",{"#":"sound crack"},{"#":"anim fall"},"^Three steps — the plank snaps. You fall.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.death"},null],"c-1":["\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.careful"},null]}],null],"careful":[[{"#":"anim walk_slow"},"^First plank — groans. Holds.","\n","^Second plank — flexes. Holds.","\n","^Halfway across. A darker plank ahead — wet rot.","\n","ev","str","^Step over the dark plank","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^Test it first","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n",{"#":"anim step_over"},"^Solid wood on the other side. Good.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.success"},null],"c-1":["\n","^You press with your toe. It crumbles.","\n",["ev","str","^Step over the gap","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n",{"#":"anim step_over_gap"},{"->":"room3_bridge.success"},null]}],null]}],null],"success":[{"#":"sound footstep_solid"},{"#":"anim reach_ground"},"^Solid ground. You made it.","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"fear_understood"},"/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^<i>Fear wasn't weakness. It was paying attention. It kept you safe.</i>","\n","^<b>VOICE:</b> ...you might be right. i'll think about it.","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"karma"},2,"+",{"VAR=":"karma","re":true},"/ev",{"->":".^.^.^.8"},null]}],"nop","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"fear_mislabeled"},"/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^<i>You ignored the fear. But you were careful anyway. Your body knew better than the voice.</i>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.14"},null]}],"nop","\n",{"->":"room4_garden"},null],"death":[["ev",{"VAR?":"deaths"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"deaths","re":true},"/ev","ev",{"VAR?":"bridge_freeze_count"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"bridge_freeze_count","re":true},"/ev",{"#":"visual bardo_flash"},{"#":"music bardo_hum"},"^...falling...","\n","ev","str","^...","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n",{"#":"visual rotten_bridge"},"^You're at the bridge again. Your body remembers.","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bridge_freeze_count"},1,"==","/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^<b>VOICE:</b> fear froze you. told you.","\n","^<i>No. Fear WARNED you. You just didn't listen carefully enough.</i>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.10"},null]}],"nop","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.cross"},null]}],null]}],"room4_garden":[[{"#":"music garden_dying"},{"#":"visual dying_trees"},"^Six trees in a circle. Three dead. Three dying.","\n","^You can burn the dead (fuel + fire) or purify the living (water).","\n","ev","str","^Gather dry bark from dead trees","/str",{"VAR?":"has_fuel"},"!","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":5},"ev","str","^Find water behind collapsed shed","/str",{"VAR?":"has_water"},"!","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":5},"ev","str","^Burn the dead trees","/str",{"VAR?":"has_fuel"},"/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":5},"ev","str","^Pour water on the living trees","/str",{"VAR?":"has_water"},"/ev",{"*":".^.c-3","flg":5},"ev","str","^Leave the garden alone","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-4","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n","ev",1,"/ev",{"VAR=":"has_fuel","re":true},"^<i>Dry. Burns fast.</i>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^"},null],"c-1":["\n",{"#":"anim move_rubble"},"^A rain barrel. Half full. A cracked bowl to carry it.","\n","ev",1,"/ev",{"VAR=":"has_water","re":true},"^<i>It leaks. Have to move fast.</i>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^"},null],"c-2":["\n",{"->":".^.^.^.burn"},null],"c-3":["\n",{"->":".^.^.^.purify"},null],"c-4":["\n",{"->":".^.^.^.ignore"},null]}],{"burn":[{"#":"anim light_fire"},{"#":"sound fire_roar"},{"#":"visual trees_