ng. guess which one the world rewards?","\n",["ev","str","^Satisfaction","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^Say nothing","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n","^<b>VOICE:</b> and what's the reward for getting stronger?","\n",["ev","str","^Rest","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^More strength","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},"ev","str","^I don't know","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n","^<b>VOICE:</b> ...cute. but no. the reward is never resting again. you get stronger so you can carry more. forever.","\n","^<i>That can't be right. Can it?</i>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.^.^.g-0"},null],"c-1":["\n","^<b>VOICE:</b> exactly. the treadmill never stops. isn't that exciting?","\n","^<i>It sounds exhausting.</i>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.^.^.g-0"},null],"c-2":["\n","^<b>VOICE:</b> you will.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.^.^.g-0"},null]}],null],"c-1":["\n","^...","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-0"},null]}],null],"g-0":["^<i>Petals keep falling. You don't know where you're going. But you can stand when you're ready.</i>","\n",{"#":"sound save_chime"},{"->":"zone1_end"},null]}],null]}],"zone1_end":[{"#":"music zone1_complete"},{"#":"visual title_card"},"^<i>Zone 1 — Complete</i>","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"has_joy_petal"},"/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^<i>Joy petal: collected</i>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.8"},null]}],"nop","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"kodama_choice"},"str","^burn","/str","==","/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^<i>The garden burned.</i>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.18"},null]}],"nop","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"kodama_choice"},"str","^purify","/str","==","/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^<i>The garden drank.</i>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.28"},null]}],"nop","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"kodama_choice"},"str","^ignore","/str","==","/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^<i>The garden waited.</i>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.38"},null]}],"nop","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"fear_understood"},"/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^<i>Fear: understood as alarm, not weakness</i>